<typeStatus id="54A0758FFFF7FFCFFBB9F8EEFB4F72E4" box="[1087,1189,1906,1932]" pageId="11" pageNumber="124">holotype</typeStatus>
. We found seven sheets of this collection, including three from P. Here we complete the lectotypification of this species by designating the specimen P00721677 as the 
<typeStatus id="54A0758FFFF7FFCFFBE8F84DFB3D7283" box="[1134,1239,2001,2027]" pageId="11" pageNumber="124">lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
